Rulings.Base:
1. Special Summoning this card from your hand is a Trigger Effect.
2. You cannot Special Summon this card during the Damage Step.
3. If you have this card and "Meklord Emperor Skiel" in your hand when your 'Blackwing' monster is destroyed and sent to the GY, you can only Special Summon 1 of them.
4. The 'Blackwing' monster being destroyed and sent to the GY must be the last thing to occur if you want to Special Summon this card from your hand.
5. "Solemn Judgment" can negate a Synchro Summon that is using this card as a Synchro Material Monster.
